<div class="row" id="intro">
	<div class="col-xs-12 welcome">
		<h1 id="welcome-line-1">
			Welcome to the
		</h1>
		<h1 id="welcome-line-2">
			Duke Innovative Design Agency
		</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12">
		<p id="description">
			The only student-run marketing and design center for student organizations at Duke University
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-xs-12">
			<i class="icon-angle-down icon-4x" id="intro-down"></i>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row" id="why">
	<div class="col-xs-12 home-header">
		<h1 class="header-h1">Why DiDA?</h1>
		<p class="lead header-lead">Isn't it obvious?</p>
	</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
		<img src="satisfaction.svg">
		<p class="why-text">We're freakin' talented.<br>Satisfaction guaranteed.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
		<img src="free.svg">
		<p class="why-text">Our services are free to<br>undergraduate student organizations.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-xs-12 down">
			<i class="icon-angle-down icon-4x" id="why-down"></i>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row" id="services">
	<div class="col-xs-12 home-header">
		<h1 class="header-h1">We can design anything.</h1>
		<p class="lead header-lead">You name it, we'll design it.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="row" id="services-content">
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 services-group" id="services-group-1">
			<div class="services-banner-container">
				<div class="l-triangle-top services-ribbon-top-1"></div>
				<div class="l-triangle-bottom services-ribbon-bottom-1"></div>
				<div class="rectangle">
					<h3 class="services-header" id="services-header-1">Print</h3>
				</div>
				<div class="r-triangle-top services-ribbon-top-1"></div>
				<div class="r-triangle-bottom services-ribbon-bottom-1"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-xs-12 services-content">
				<p>
					Want promotional materials for your organization or an event? We'll give you a design that you can plaster all over the walls, buildings and even the students at Duke!
				</p>
				<ul class="col-xs-6">
					<li>Posters</li>
					<li>Small Flyers</li>
					<li>Large Flyers</li>
					<li>Banners</li>
					<li>The Chronicle Ads</li>
				</ul>
				<ul class="col-xs-6">
					<li>Dining Hall Table Tents</li>
					<li>Bus Ads</li>
					<li>T-Shirts</li>
					<li>Logos</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6 services-group" id="services-group-2">
			<div class="services-banner-container">
				<div class="l-triangle-top services-ribbon-top-2"></div>
				<div class="l-triangle-bottom services-ribbon-bottom-2"></div>
				<div class="rectangle">
					<h3 class="services-header" id="services-header-2">Web</h3>
				</div>
				<div class="r-triangle-top services-ribbon-top-2"></div>
				<div class="r-triangle-bottom services-ribbon-bottom-2"></div>
			</div>		
			<div class="col-xs-12 services-content">
				<p>
					Need to put up information about your organization on the internet and have it to look absolutely smashing? DiDA can help! We also offer web design consultations.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-xs-12 down">
			<i class="icon-angle-down icon-4x" id="services-down"></i>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="pull-left inset" id="announcements">
	<img src="/speech-bubble.svg" id="speech-bubble">
	<div id="announcement-text">
		<b>Announcements</b>
		<p>No more plaza boards!</p>
	</div>
	<img src="/sad.svg" id="sad">
</div>
